---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contractor Software Hub" description="Independent, honest reviews of contractor software. No vendor copy. No padding. Just honest calls on what each tool costs, what it gets right, and who it's wrong for.">

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="bg-[#0f172a] text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-[#22c55e] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Independent Software Reviews</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; color: white;">
        Most contractor software reviews are useless.<br />
        <span class="text-[#22c55e]">These aren't.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        No vendor copy. No padding. Just an honest call on what each tool costs, what it gets right, and who it's actually wrong for — written for contractors running 1–50 people, not enterprise.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-[#22c55e] text-[#0f172a] font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#16a34a] transition">
          Start with Jobber →
        </a>
        <a href="#by-trade" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-gray-500 text-gray-300 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:border-white hover:text-white transition">
          Browse by Trade
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Top Picks / Most Read -->
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Most Read Reviews</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mt-1">Not sure where to start? These are the ones contractors look up most.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <!-- Jobber -->
    <a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Jobber</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $49/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">The best all-around field service software for contractors running 1–25 employees.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#dcfce7] text-[#166534] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">⭐ Top Pick</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">8.8/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- Housecall Pro -->
    <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Housecall Pro</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $65/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">Best mobile app in the category. Built-in review requests on most plans.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#dcfce7] text-[#166534] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">Strong Pick</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">8.4/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <!-- ServiceTitan -->
    <a href="/blog/servicetitan-review/" class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold text-[#475569]">ST</div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-lg group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">ServiceTitan</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">From $398/mo</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">Enterprise-grade for contractors doing $1M+ in revenue with 10+ employees.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#e2e8f0] text-[#475569] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">Specialist</span>
        <span class="text-xs bg-[#fef3c7] text-[#92400e] px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">7.9/10</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Head-to-Head Comparisons -->
<section class="bg-[#f8fafc] border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Head-to-Head Comparisons</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Deciding between two tools? These cut straight to the call.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/jobber-vs-housecall-pro/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
          <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold">vs</span>
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Jobber vs Housecall Pro</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Best for most vs best mobile app</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/servicetitan-vs-jobber/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#475569]">ST</div>
          <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold">vs</span>
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">ServiceTitan vs Jobber</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Enterprise vs small team</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-vs-fieldedge/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#be185d]">H</div>
          <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs font-semibold">vs</span>
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#fef3c7] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-[#92400e]">FE</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">HCP vs FieldEdge</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Easy setup vs QuickBooks depth</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- By Trade -->
<section id="by-trade" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
  <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Best Software by Trade</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Trade-specific roundups for the tools that actually work in your field.</p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
    <a href="/blog/hvac-software/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔧</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">HVAC</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">7 options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/plumbing-software/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔩</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Plumbing</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">5 options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/roofing-software/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🏠</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Roofing</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">5 options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/landscaping-software/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🌿</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Landscaping</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">6 options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/pest-control-software/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🐛</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Pest Control</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">5 options</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/best-software-painting-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-center hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
      <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🎨</div>
      <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Painting</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">5 options</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- By Category -->
<section class="bg-[#f8fafc] border-y border-gray-200">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Best Software by Category</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Roundups organized by the business function you're trying to improve.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <a href="/blog/best-estimating-software-small-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg">📊</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Estimating (Small)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Best for small contractors</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-estimating-software-general-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fef3c7] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🏗️</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Estimating (GC)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">For general contractors</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-scheduling-software-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#dcfce7] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg">📅</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">Scheduling</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">6 best options</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-crm-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg">👥</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">CRM</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Customer management tools</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog/best-cad-software-contractors/" class="group p-5 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#f3e8ff] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-lg">✏️</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold group-hover:text-[#1C2B4B]">CAD Software</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Design & drafting tools</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Trust / Methodology -->
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
  <div class="bg-[#1C2B4B] rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-white">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; color: white;">The work behind the call</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mb-8">
      Most contractor software reviews skip the hard part. Here's what actually goes into each one on this site.
    </p>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-5 bg-white/10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🧪</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">We sign up for trials</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Every tool gets tested hands-on, not just reviewed from a vendor demo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white/10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">💰</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">We analyze pricing honestly</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Real pricing, including hidden fees and contract terms that vendors don't advertise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 bg-white/10 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📝</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-white">We read hundreds of reviews</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">G2, Capterra, and industry forums to find patterns in real contractor feedback.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
